// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0211 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: f8ec86ea-3a09-532e-b9f8-f1269342551d

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:2*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
